{"items":[{"term":"毋甘","pronunciation":"m̄-kam","definition":"動詞／形容詞。捨不得；不忍心；對某人或某物有深切愛惜而不願耗用或失去。","fieldNote":"媽媽有一瓶香水，是美國阿姨探親那年帶回來的。放在梳妝台最裡面的抽屜，開過幾次，每次開了又蓋回去。我問她為什麼不用，她說「毋甘」。\n\n阿姨後來就沒有再回來了。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/879/","imageAlt":"毋甘","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-480.webp 480w, assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-768.webp 768w, assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/46adb7aa09a635cc-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"拍損","pronunciation":"phah-sńg","definition":"動詞。使物件毀壞；浪費（物力、食物、時間）；糟蹋。","fieldNote":"阿嬤從廚房探出頭，看我把吃剩的便當倒進廚餘桶，皺著眉說「拍損」。不是罵，是疼。那種疼裡面，有她整個年代。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/4119/","imageAlt":"拍損","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/749c73b758574876-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/749c73b758574876-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/749c73b758574876-480.webp 480w, assets/images/749c73b758574876-768.webp 768w, assets/images/749c73b758574876-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/749c73b758574876-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"好玄","pronunciation":"hònn-hiân","definition":"形容詞。對於不了解的事物感到新奇，產生興趣或想進一步探究。","fieldNote":"小時候颱風天停電，阿公點蠟燭。火苗在風中晃，把每個人影投在牆上像皮影戲。我蹲在桌腳，伸手去碰我自己的影子。影子也伸手。我把手放遠一點，影子變大；放近，變小。阿公在旁邊笑說「囡仔人就是好玄」。風還在叫，但我已經忘了害怕。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/14002/","imageAlt":"好玄","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-480.webp 480w, assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-768.webp 768w, assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/e0a26e22482c86d9-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"數念","pronunciation":"siàu-liām","definition":"動詞。想念、掛念、懷念。","fieldNote":"姑姑嫁去日本十年了。每次打電話回來，阿嬤從來不主動講「我想妳」。她講菜市場誰誰誰漲價、隔壁的狗生了幾隻、今年的芒果收得好。講完一輪才說「恁彼爿會寒無？」掛電話以後，她在客廳坐很久。沒有開電視。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/11122/","imageAlt":"數念","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-480.webp 480w, assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-768.webp 768w, assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/ccefcae19e269940-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"月眉","pronunciation":"gue̍h-bâi","definition":"名詞。農曆初三、初四的新月，形狀彎細像眉毛，故名月眉。","fieldNote":"山上的家，門口就是石階一階一階往下走。晚上吃完飯，阿公會帶我站在最高那一階乘涼。山風從谷底吹上來。他抬手往對面山稜線一指，說「彼叫月眉」。一道細細的鉤掛在山頂上。我以為月亮只有一種——圓的。原來它也會慢慢長大，從一道眉毛開始。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/998/","imageAlt":"月眉","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-480.webp 480w, assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-768.webp 768w, assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/2129ffa14eddd733-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"相借問","pronunciation":"sio-tsioh-mn̄g","definition":"動詞。打招呼、寒喧；互相打招呼問候。","fieldNote":"小時候跟阿嬤去菜市場，從巷口走到攤前不到一百公尺，她要相借問三、四次。賣魚的、賣菜的、隔壁的隔壁的鄰居，每個都停下來「食飽未？」「欲買啥？」。我覺得煩，拉她的手叫她快走。她說「人佮人，就是按呢才袂生分」。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/5262/","imageAlt":"相借問","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-480.webp 480w, assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-768.webp 768w, assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/846221b93ac7538a-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"白鑠鑠","pronunciation":"pe̍h-siak-siak","definition":"形容詞（疊字）。形容白得發亮、刺眼的白。","fieldNote":"開學第一天，新買的制服掛在椅背上，白鑠鑠的，連衣領都還沒被汗濕過。媽媽前一晚燙過，皺褶還挺著。早上穿上身，硬得像紙板。走進校門才發現，學長學姐的襯衫都已經奶白色了，只有我們這群新生，遠遠看過去是一排刺眼的白。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/tshiau/?lui=tai_su&tsha=白鑠鑠","imageAlt":"白鑠鑠","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-480.webp 480w, assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-768.webp 768w, assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/f45fd4ce2126d9ce-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"四序","pronunciation":"sù-sī","definition":"形容詞。井井有條、妥當；讓人覺得舒服安適的感覺。","fieldNote":"過年前的下午，阿嬤把所有的棉被翻出來曬。傍晚收進來，一床一床拍平、摺好、疊回櫃子。最後一床壓進去，她後退一步看了看，嘴角微微動一下，說「按呢就四序矣」。整個下午的灰塵和陽光味，都關進了櫃子裡。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/1473/","imageAlt":"四序","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-480.webp 480w, assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-768.webp 768w, assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/83a2f2959d744fe1-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}},{"term":"日頭赤焱焱，隨人顧性命","pronunciation":"Ji̍t-thâu tshiah-iānn-iānn, suî-lâng kòo sènn-miā","definition":"俗諺。大太陽底下，人各自顧自己的命，無力顧及他人。形容人在患難或困境中，以自我保護為主要考量。","fieldNote":"暑假的中午，外面沒有人。連狗都不見了。柏油路面的熱氣一陣一陣往上竄，公車站牌在那裡站著，沒有人等。大人說「日頭赤焱焱」，說這個時候出去是在找死。我趴在窗台往外看，整條街靜著，只有一輛機車遠遠駛過，司機縮著頭。","sensoryTags":["未分類"],"sourceUrl":"https://sutian.moe.edu.tw/zh-hant/su/26953/","imageAlt":"日頭赤焱焱，隨人顧性命","image":{"fallback":"assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-1536.jpg","src":"assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-1536.webp","srcset":"assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-480.webp 480w, assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-768.webp 768w, assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-1200.webp 1200w, assets/images/c39b0ab9de6708c8-1536.webp 1536w","width":1536,"height":1024}}]}
